      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Filipao Nunes is a multi-disciplinary agency based in Monterrey, Mexico working on residential and business architecture and interior design projects. The studio was looking for a portfolio that fit with their new branding and displayed their work to primarily serve as a work reference for future clients."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Business Details",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Filipao Nunes is an upcoming agency that has succeeded at penetrating the high-end business and residential market in Monterrey, Mexico. He is mostly known for his residential work and high-end restaurants and night clubs."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "For the past several years the studio had been working without a website and without a definite branding. With the studio’s recent success, the studio has been busy building a team, establishing new offices, and defining their identity. Nation Visuals, a multi-disciplinary agency in Monterrey focusing on branding, helped Filipao Nunes design the studio’s branding and photograph and document a select group of projects to feature on the studio’s portfolio."
        },
